}}'''Andorra''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was added to [[BitLife: Life Simulator|BitLife]] in July 10, 2022.

On July 10, 2022, new countries were added to both iOS and Android. Along with Andorra, there was also [[Angola]], [[Aruba]], [[Belize]], [[El Salvador]], [[Guatemala]], [[Guyana]], [[Haiti]], [[Nicaragua]], [[Papua New Guinea]], [[Paraguay]], [[Samoa]], [[Tunisia]], and [[Uganda]]. This was added in a bug fix update prior to the upcoming Business Update.

==Information==

==Vital Statistics==



Currency:  Euro (€)

Default Cities: Andorra la Vella, Encamp, La Massana

Graduation Age:  18

Minimum Age to Drop out of School:  16

Free University:  No

Minimum Legal Driving Age:  18

Same-Sex Dating Legal:  Yes

Same-Sex Marriage Legal: Yes

Changing Last Name After Marriage Permitted: Yes

Free Healthcare: No

Gambling Legal: Yes

Death Penalty Legal: 

Conjugal Visits Permitted: No

Commercial Surrogacy Legal: Yes

